<section><title>Description</title>
<!--use <ref> on all component names (other than the one indexed from this file) in this section only-->
  <p>The <tag>pluralize</tag><idx><tag>pluralize</tag></idx> component renders the enclosed text in plural form.  If the plural form of the text component is irregular, the unique spelling can be specified with the <attr>pluralForm</attr> attribute.  If the text is designed to alter based on a varying numerical value, the <attr>basedOnNumber</attr> should be used. 
 See examples below.</p>
</section> 

  
